	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.30]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Just to clarify, Divine Aura will not clear the hate list.&nbsp;&nbsp;You won't be attacked if the mob can attack someone else.  If the mob hates you more than anyone else and you are close, you will be attacked again after you remove the DA buff.  It used to be that you could keep agro by sitting underneath the mob due to sitting agro.  It still works despite agro changes, but you need to be very low health and sitting to keep agro even while DAed (or the last one left alive).  I have some nice logs showing me (cleric) tanking Ixiblat Fer and Lady Vox for over 15 seconds before I chickened out and stood up and ran out of range (it didn't help enough with Vox though :/ ).<br><br>You can't cast spells, use items or attack while you are Invulnerable.  You can be Death-Touched while &quot;Invulnerable&quot;.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
